The paper presents a new mechanism for logical theory acquisition using a neural forward-chaining differentiable rule induction network. This approach is neuro-symbolic, which suggests it could fall under cs.AI. The paper also mentions the use of dense vector representations, which is a common technique in machine learning and could place it under cs.LG. The use of natural language processing techniques to extract logical rules could also place it under cs.CL. The paper also mentions the use of neural networks, which could place it under cs.NE. Finally, the paper deals with logical rule induction and theory learning, which suggests it could fall under cs.LO.
